{"tid":775470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★「不誠實取用電腦罪」成絕響？　戴啟思指時有誤用　促另行立法","createTime":"2018-08-11T07:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T10:05:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1df2d4c3d128594033bbcf5131beed1dcd6043b1","tid":775470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1738583/org/cb1b020468e2171af8646c93f8850cc1.jpg/FavGl9eH3TEHq5C9DOZjl2NJ-bkQDoklkaCC3ZGggt0?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1738583%2Forg%2Fcb1b020468e2171af8646c93f8850cc1.jpg%2FFavGl9eH3TEHq5C9DOZjl2NJ-bkQDoklkaCC3ZGggt0%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=e0611e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前數名小學教師被發現涉嫌以手機洩露小一入學叩門試題，惟數人「不誠實取用電腦」的控罪被裁定不成立，律政司提上訴亦被駁回。有傳媒就引述消息指，律政司在參考判詞後，暫停涉及智能電話罪行案件的檢控程序，令外界擔憂如「偷拍裙底」等涉及智能電話的罪行難以被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會主席戴啟思接受《香港01》電話訪問時承認，「不誠實意圖而取用電腦控罪」有時被錯誤地運用，但他強調，有關控罪沒有被濫用。他建議港府參考蘇格蘭的情況，引入新法例處理有關罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/221441/%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%BD%AA-%E6%88%90%E7%B5%95%E9%9F%BF-%E6%88%B4%E5%95%9F%E6%80%9D%E6%8C%87%E6%99%82%E6%9C%89%E8%AA%A4%E7%94%A8-%E4%BF%83%E5%8F%A6%E8%A1%8C%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F221441%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B5%2595%25E9%259F%25BF-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%2595%259F%25E6%2580%259D%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%258F%25A6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595&d=GJcPMEruID2M0yd6UrIIRgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5be6279d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/221441/%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%BD%AA-%E6%88%90%E7%B5%95%E9%9F%BF-%E6%88%B4%E5%95%9F%E6%80%9D%E6%8C%87%E6%99%82%E6%9C%89%E8%AA%A4%E7%94%A8-%E4%BF%83%E5%8F%A6%E8%A1%8C%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95</a>"},{"pid":"2d5665c6c46504d48627a34204f1a2f85812d91b","tid":775470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"不誠實取用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">電力</span>罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97a2e7fb3dd91730c290f9613d60e9990eedc49","tid":775470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"不誠實取用IT device"},{"pid":"73272a0ae784894c25d92208dabc4d9fcc8aae82","tid":775470,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"老貓post游B改圖，不誠實使用游B圖，石丸擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1595b973be1063aa61b184fb2260beda2924a7f6","tid":775470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73272a0ae784894c25d92208dabc4d9fcc8aae82","tid":775470,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"老貓post游B改圖，不誠實使用游B圖，石丸擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c18fb4535714345443c6a95d11f11426a4134cf","tid":775470,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"不誠實上forum 9up罪"},{"pid":"0e263f65ee539cd4c2e026052b1887b367841e92","tid":775470,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:54:38.000Z","msg":"誠實使用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce747dc6534dcd61e6edd1cf26e05de50f8eeac8","tid":775470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e263f65ee539cd4c2e026052b1887b367841e92","tid":775470,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score